This paper discusses a dataset version control system and a platform for collaborative data analysis. It involves managing large datasets and dealing with divergent collections of data, which are common challenges in database systems (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of algorithms for searching and analyzing data (cs.DS, cs.IR) and machine learning techniques for collaborative data analysis (cs.LG).
